data.description: Truly turn-key horse property only 8 minutes to the World Equestrian Center & major shopping centers! Enter through the gates of this private 5 acre property boasting a large 4 bedroom/ 3 bathroom updated home, 6 stalls, 120' x 200' irrigated fiber arena, 4 generous 3 board fenced paddocks, large detached garage/work shop, tack room, wash stall, RV hook up, 2 wells & more. This primely located property is on a quiet dead-end road & high & dry. The concrete block brick house has an attached 2 car garage & has been updated with a newer roof, flooring, paint, 6' gutters, light fixtures, renovated bathrooms & has a large kitchen, huge walk-in pantry & plenty of storage space. The barn has a washer & dryer & there are 4, 12' x 13' stalls & 2, 10' x 14' stalls, covered viewing area & hay shed. The property is ready for you to move in & bring your horses!
